scene.message:
Toro: No way... only milk and{nl}
cheese left, and I don't even{nl}
get to stress-eat...{waitkey}{clearbox}I can't even have dairy...{nl}
It's a plot by someone who{nl}
knows that. Yeah, that's{nl}
gotta be it!!{waitkey}{clearbox}The whole world's laughing at{nl}
my misfortune! U... ugh......{nl}
dammit~{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: Huh, huh, whaa? Why was{nl}
I sleeping in a place like{nl}
this?{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh stop, everyone, don't look{nl}
at me like that — it's{nl}
embarrassing...{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: U... ugh...... why is it{nl}
always me this happens to...{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh right, I almost forgot.{nl}
Kuroori asked me to hand{nl}
these to you.{waitkey}{clearbox}When we came back from the{nl}
tower together, he picked up{nl}
some glittering shards,{waitkey}{clearbox}but his muscles ache so badly{nl}
he can't carry things, so I'm{nl}
delivering them for him.{waitkey}{ret}

Toro: I'm not the only one{nl}
having a hard time, right.{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase and you are giving it{nl}
your all too.{waitkey}{clearbox}All right! I'll work hard too,{nl}
and learn to drink milk!!{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Kenta Yokouchi{nl}
Nicknamed Toro. Loves to eat.{nl}
Strong, but timid at heart.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Student: It suddenly froze{nl}
over — is this the demons'{nl}
doing too?{waitkey}{clearbox}I just checked, and there's{nl}
hardly any food left.{waitkey}{clearbox}No wonder Toro panicked...{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Huh? Whether I went{nl}
to fetch a teacher?{waitkey}{clearbox}I did! But nobody would{nl}
listen — "it'll fix itself,"{nl}
"I'm busy," and so on.{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, anyway, I'm glad it's{nl}
safe.{waitkey}The food, that is.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Dumped by the girl{nl}
he likes, forced to drink the{nl}
milk he hates — Toro's having{nl}
no luck today.{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, everyone has days like{nl}
this now and then.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: That classroom that{nl}
wouldn't open — you know, way{nl}
to the left out of here.{waitkey}{clearbox}The ice melted a bit, so you{nl}
can get in now, they say.{waitkey}{clearbox}There's a rumor a gorgeous{nl}
orb is floating in there. Is{nl}
it safe to go near, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: This is no time to be{nl}
loafing around here!{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's go find someone we can{nl}
rely on!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: We've gathered the{nl}
"Mirror Shards," so let's{nl}
hurry to the courtyard!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Uesugi's not here.{nl}
Wasn't he supposed to be{nl}
watching Toro?{waitkey}{clearbox}That guy — did he bail?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What's with him, over{nl}
being dumped by a girl! He'll{nl}
never amount to anything like{nl}
that.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That big eater —{nl}
something came out of his{nl}
stomach, but is he all{nl}
right now?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Bwa~~~~choo!{waitkey}Ah, sorry — did it get on your{nl}
clothes?{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly, I feel as blue as a{nl}
head of lettuce gone limp in{nl}
the fridge.{waitkey}{clearbox}I figured I'd eat some{nl}
piping-hot ramen, but the{nl}
water won't even boil.{waitkey}{clearbox}On top of that, Toro went on{nl}
a rampage, swearing to scarf{nl}
down all the cafeteria food{nl}
to spite getting dumped.{waitkey}{clearbox}So I hurried and hid{nl}
everything but the dairy.{waitkey}{clearbox}No telling what'll happen{nl}
next, so — that's me being{nl}
ahead of the game, eh?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: The whole school's in a{nl}
panic, and the teachers have{nl}
it rough too, seems like.{waitkey}{clearbox}Dunno what you did, but I'm{nl}
glad things settled down.{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, me and one other guy{nl}
will keep watch from here, so{nl}
you can rest easy.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Toro suddenly vanished,{nl}
and the next thing I knew{waitkey}{clearbox}he started babbling nonsense{nl}
about milk and torture.{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, me and one other guy{nl}
will keep watch, so you can{nl}
rest easy.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: A Persona, huh... Used{nl}
right, it seems like you could{nl}
do anything.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Personas are scary,{nl}
huh. Me, I'm the very picture{nl}
of selflessness, so I'm{nl}
totally fine, though.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Ayase landed us in a{nl}
right mess. Honestly, that{nl}
girl.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: A room with a beautiful{nl}
orb floating in it? It seems{nl}
worth a look.{waitkey}{ret}
